            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingOne">
                    <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                        data-bs-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseOne">
                        <strong>Week-1 : Introduction to System Testing </strong>
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingOne"
                    data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
                    <div class="collapse-overview">

                        <div class="collapse-item">
                            <strong>Definition and scope of system testing</strong>
                        </div>
                        <div class="collapse-item">
                            <strong>Differences between unit testing, integration testing, and system testing</strong>
                        </div>
                        <div class="collapse-item">
                            <strong>Importance of system testing in the software development lifecycle</strong>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>

